{"tid":1629533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一田同埋富邦銀行都係新鴻基擁有.","createTime":"2019-10-06T09:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T10:54:16.000Z","uid":315125,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5884ab6c2b79373a3dfac80fec5dc138ba9a71f2","tid":1629533,"uid":315125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"各位兄弟<br />\n大家知唔知道一田係新鴻基全資擁有, 同埋富邦銀行都係."},{"pid":"91731e54d94dc0ff12971440b2f40a418ea898b9","tid":1629533,"uid":169646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"又想吹風叫人去裝修? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4455f98b441deec78943f8f334c37463962e55e4","tid":1629533,"uid":87672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:41:18.000Z","msg":"富邦台資黎"},{"pid":"d6d7e22e00d1bce45d361d898fa75930a2cc3481","tid":1629533,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"又係鬼account"},{"pid":"a09e29bb90fd0032891c3ffeddb963116a39ae0f","tid":1629533,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"P牌仔"},{"pid":"d9686603ed0b0cfafd072303deaca31f41749144","tid":1629533,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"流料真係唔知，仲有咩山埃即管吹出嚟"},{"pid":"19fd5c7bfc9a71de7cc765933135c4c7f8018e0e","tid":1629533,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:43:24.000Z","msg":"富邦台灣嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79065ea3534368cab586f59d6cce28bb7f452f0","tid":1629533,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:44:36.000Z","msg":"P for rubbish"},{"pid":"c4af391d85f02f0a67e8193f5a4ef041deb347ed","tid":1629533,"uid":322937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:45:38.000Z","msg":"富邦台灣大銀行黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a7f97762aeeb2c61f5e134c9f559429ca366f7","tid":1629533,"uid":105176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:50:55.000Z","msg":"喂呀sir 屌你老母"},{"pid":"7cff0edba547126f8547a2617b8f35edb3390f90","tid":1629533,"uid":315125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:52:39.000Z","msg":"消息真確無誤<br />\n有家人喺一田裏面做, 已經係超過一年前嘅消息, 集團高層曾向內部公佈 &quot;日股東已賣曬所有股份比新鴻基&quot; , 同時再發表富邦銀行係佢哋自己公司嘅."},{"pid":"c6904d82c388b3f44507d435b484d5f4a1b8e121","tid":1629533,"uid":196130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"sir, this way."},{"pid":"335071c9552c223b36b5324eeee31d2c6e63f30a","tid":1629533,"uid":315125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:00:23.000Z","msg":"至於光大同新鴻基嘅關係, 相信講大家都知道.<br />\n<br />\n富邦銀行<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fubonbank.com.hk/tc/about-us/corporate-profile.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fubonbank.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-us%2Fcorporate-profile.html&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=5185cd53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fubonbank.com.hk/tc/about-us/corporate-profile.html</a><br />\n富邦銀行（香港）有限公司（「富邦銀行」）是富邦金融控股股份有限公司（「富邦金控」）的全資附屬公司。富邦金控為台灣最大的金融控股公司之一，也是唯一在「兩岸三地均擁有銀行子行」的台資金融機構，擁有最完整的金融服務平台。<strong>富邦金控自港基國際銀行（「港基」）兩大股東 &mdash; Arab Banking Corporation (B.S.C.) 及中國光大控股有限公司 &mdash; 收購港基 75% 股權後，於 2005 年 4 月 6 日正式把港基易名為富邦銀行；並於2011年6月將富邦銀行成功私有化，成為富邦金控的全資附屬公司。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出自維基百科，自由嘅百科全書<br />\nJump to navigationJump to search<br />\n富邦銀行 (香港) 歷史<br />\n呢間銀行喺1970年代初創立，叫過做新鴻基銀行、港基國際銀行。1993年11月，當時嘅港基國際銀行喺香港聯合交易所上市。2005年4月6號，改名做富邦銀行（香港）有限公司。"},{"pid":"ea440a31fb21983257c0a158a19065eaf24eb5f2","tid":1629533,"uid":315125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4455f98b441deec78943f8f334c37463962e55e4","tid":1629533,"uid":87672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor